Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:20.35,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:26.60,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:31.90,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:38.41,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:45.04,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:51.38,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:06.35,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:13.11,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:19.36,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:25.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rise back up again and again and again
