Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.55,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have Hattori sit there.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.01,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he had some things to talk about, like the contract and the assistants.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats on the serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.16,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Why is someone else here?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.32,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Does it have something to do with the contract?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Miura. I've been with Jack since last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.99,0:00:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.91,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura will be supervising you two from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have a place to work?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We got it from a relative who's a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? How's the rent?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.93,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kawaguchi Tarou's workplace, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cheap; about as much as the utility bills—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,[hard to read?],You could have rented a room with your sign-on bonus, but you've saved yourselves the trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, great!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.35,0:02:51.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be in such a rush.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we have to discuss the transfer.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shady Detective Trap{\i0} will be supervised by Miura, not me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.99,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of other serializations\N and also just took over One Piece.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be a good idea to just\N hand them off to someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.09,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he was assigned to this new project.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we've been together until now...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there absolutely no way you can do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't uncommon.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.85,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago, even a veteran author had their supervisor switched on them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.02,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They protested to their editors, but were convinced eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.61,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably wouldn't even listen\N if new guys like you complained.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright! I'll do my best! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in your care.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to keep a serialization going.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, I'll leave them to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori sure is cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be unusual for this to happen, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.36,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, he was begging so desperately to be allowed to work on Ashirogi Muto,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they got angry with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything until now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better show me a good manga!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle said it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.65,0:05:07.70,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything about an editor change, and getting used to one takes a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the reality of being a professional.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.49,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it bothers me that supervisors are like lottery tickets; you could end up with a winner or a loser.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori was definitely a winner.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, am I a loser?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still only 23!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine our youthful spirits and go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contractual salary is that high?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much for you high schoolers.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.77,0:05:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you needed a place to work, we'd give you more money, but you guys already have one.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,[UNREADABLE!!],So you're not actually getting that amount.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.49,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, your script payment is ¥12,000 per page, with a 50% color page bonus.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I heard it was ¥9,000 for new authors.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for non-serialized work. For serializations, it's ¥12,000.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, stop interrupting and listen. These are the arrangements.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The copyright belongs to Yueisha.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No other magazine may publish your work.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time to \Ndraw for another magazine!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the opposite; since we\N have an annual contract,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make sure it runs continuously for the whole year.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring a proper contract next time, so you can sign it then.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also the problem of your assistants,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.19,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I managed to get a pro \Nnamed Ogawa. He's talented.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.74,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have many new people, so I've got no other talented people to give you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anyone you know who could help you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who dabbles in manga or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.70,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Acquaintances?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.83,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Ishizawa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.87,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Having someone assist you with the\N inking and tone would help a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our last resort.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find two young people \Nwith serious personalities.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, how much does it cost for an assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's important.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A young assistant costs ¥10,000 per day.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,About ¥160,000 per month \Nworking four days per week.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At the most, Ogawa would \Ncost you ¥380,000 per month.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,¥380,000?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.90,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, you can only pull people in with that kind of salary, so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires a high skill level, and he'll direct and supervise the other assistants for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, assistants have \Nexpenses like travel and food.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Until it's published, we're in the red!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If it gets canceled before \Nthen, we'll stay in the red!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't talk about being in debt when we've just been serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, is it alright if they stay over here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only enough space in the next room to nap.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.72,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle did a gag manga, so the assistants just went home the next day.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle was successful enough\N for assistants? What's his name?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's Kawaguchi Tarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The author of that {\i1}Super Hero Legend {\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why that poster's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So that work was born here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I really loved it when I read it in middle school!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so impressed!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting even more from you now that I know your uncle is Kawaguchi Tarou!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next comes the schedule.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadline is two weeks before Jack goes on sale.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, two weeks before \Nthe Monday that the issue is released.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.80,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideally, we want the finished \Nmanuscript by the Friday before that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The final deadline for {\i1}Trap{\i0} is February 4th.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The first chapter is 54 pages.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The second is 27.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It really only has to be 25, \Nbut you wanted a bit more?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to turn that in as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to wait for the survey results for chapter 4 onward, so we won't get into those yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,[UNREADABLE!!],Are you fine with the assistants starting at the beginning of the year?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.00,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He's going through this so fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.58,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Is this guy a winner?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you lose to them!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.36,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru Kazuya of {\i1}Otters 11{\i0} \Nis new, like us, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't met him yet,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,[hard to read?],but according to the editorial department, he quit his job as a salary man to do manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Quitting an office job?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.51,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that at the age of 26, he suddenly quit his job and started drawing manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without having read much manga before then,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.72,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,his first work got honorable mention in a monthly contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A genius on another level like Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Great things are expected from him more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.07,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,More than anyone else?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.45,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,More than Eiji?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.91,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otters{\i0} is a gag manga,\N and it has a different writing style.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no use comparing\N different manga with each other!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All that matters is that yours is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give it our all!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! You guys are still young!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna flare up and burn out!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we don't want to burn out...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was a slip of the tongue.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.06,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Is he a winner or loser?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem like a bad guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,January 17th is the New Year's party.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,New Year's party?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we invited too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All serialized mangakas attend!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If authors don't attend without a good reason,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the editors in charge of \Nthem won't have it easy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,New Year's party...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy, but nervous \Nat the same time!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem of being nervous!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, a limo will be coming to pick you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A limo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A limo's picking you up, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Serialized mangakas are pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's our first meeting\N with the assistants.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't I come then? I could do odd jobs.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd calm down if a girl was there!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.52,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There will only be five \Nmen working today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a man's workplace.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be different from before.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I'll refrain from coming by.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the chief assistant, Ogawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kato.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in your care.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.04,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say anything\N about a girl coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kato only lives 3 train stops from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be staying overnight.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a year of experience
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as an assistant in both \Nshoujo and shounen manga too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't find another person with that much experience!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.06,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get distracted if there's a girl here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.06,0:11:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly young man.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But my girlfriend...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.98,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.82,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Should we get Miyoshi to\N do the inking after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's Takahama.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's 19.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the people under me, \Nhe's the best at drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.45,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He avoided my gaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.45,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He works fast and has unlimited potential as an assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean he has no experience?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Ogawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.08,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short one desk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And a tracer.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The copier is old, but it looks like it will be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, where is the computer and printer?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.30,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Computer?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have one here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are quite a few reference books here,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's best for {\i1}Shady Detective Trap{\i0}'s\N backgrounds to be realistic.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take pictures of scenery with a digital camera, edit and trace them here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll arrange it right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, please do.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you already have a penned-in manuscript.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako, Takahama.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish up one page each.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.87,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, matching their art, \Ndraw other characters.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! So this is a pro assistant!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you weak at drawing right-facing faces?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I sketch them in reverse.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.93,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of that,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.42,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,look at the whole manuscript in reverse and check for deviances.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you're good at it, \Na little discrepancy stands out.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do most of the backgrounds and spread the work among the three of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the characters to Takahama
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and finishing will be done by \Nthe person with less work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.66,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, if the first chapter is 54 pages, and the second is 27,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we need turn this in soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He's really great!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.67,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I've got to work hard on this!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.46,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's our first serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed my brother's suit...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really that strange?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a salary man.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They said to come in everyday clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take that seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.94,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's rude to greet the authors without wearing appropriate clothes?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Ashirogi residence?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be assisting you today.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tanaka from Metropolitan Transportation.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already been waiting for 15 minutes?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he got here early to avoid being late!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,[unreadable],I feel bad for making him wait, so let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.05,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Ashirogi, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.01,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please step inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave now, we'll \Nget there 40 minutes early.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can arrange for us to \Narrive at a more suitable time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well then, we would like \Nto arrive 15 minutes early.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.44,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Being driven around like this makes me feel extra nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I need to practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Takagi, one of the mangaka duo under the name Ashirogi Muto,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,creators of the manga {\i1}Shady Detective Trap
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which will begin serialization in February.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it kind of long?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just finish with "I'm Mashiro."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should talk too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, it's not my thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.14,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this gathering \Nof suspicious black cars?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any belongings, you\N may leave them in the cloak room.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this number card with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt kinda out of place.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is some place!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.58,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If your serialization continues,\N you'll come here every year!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You get used to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma is already here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinohara-sensei! It's been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really out of place...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.85,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a belated "Happy New Year!"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in his usual sweats!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Minors mustn't drink.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of juice.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also juice.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.45,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.33,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Was there an editor who looked like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my new friend, Hiramaru-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,New friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.13,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru?! That's him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.13,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You just randomly approached me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.84,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He's the genius who might \Neven be better than Eiji!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you! We're Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you classmates of his?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alright to bring friends \Nto the New Year's party?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them are authors.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The artist and writer of Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Two in one!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of young mangakas.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I've come to a pretty strange place.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is great.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of delicious food.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I took a wrong turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on the highway, but in life.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"No way?"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to become a mangaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.87,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I want to?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment I did think that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was briefly possessed by the idea, you might say.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, when I was tired of going to work,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up an edition of Jack and thought I could do it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what the hell was I doing? I screwed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He thinks he screwed up even though he was serialized?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, bring me another!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.60,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what did you want to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't want to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I've got a monthly serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do people have to work?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to sleep and eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been born as a panda in a zoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that why it's called {\i1}Otters 11{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Subconsciously...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the otter in the aquarium is better off than a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru, there you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.38,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who flattered me by saying "You have talent!" and "You're a genius!"
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Before the party gets going,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.26,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,let's talk about the problem spots in the third chapter—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida-shi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's good to be alive?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, lets go with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The catchphrase of your third chapter...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru is kind of weird and interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to start, so come up to the front...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we were just hit by\N Hiramaru's negative aura...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative aura?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, he did say serialization was impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.08,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are certainly people who are\N uncertain when they get serialized so suddenly.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you start up, it'll all work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You two will be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.71,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.41,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for taking time out of your busy schedules to come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for allowing me to be your host for this New Year's party.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.64,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Aida Soichi, I work in Shounen Jack's editorial department.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Champagne for the toast?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pretend to drink it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice attitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.49,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,First of all, let's have a few words from Mr. Torishima of the Board of Directors.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.15,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who {\i1}Arale-chan's{\i0} Mashirito and {\i1}Super Hero Legend{\i0}'s Torishiman are based on!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Torishima.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.75,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Torishima was a model for chief\N editors while I was working there.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.09,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I was happy when he came up to me at the New Years party,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.71,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,asked "Who said you could put me in there?!", and strangled me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.96,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You were happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.96,0:18:36.92,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,388)}We're good friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.55,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And now I'm at the same New Year's party.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done already?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Another few words, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, continuing on,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.06,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask Akimoto to lead the toast on behalf of all the authors.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, you took too much—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's delicious-looking stuff over there too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you perhaps Ashirogi-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Arai. My {\i1}Baked Cheese{\i0} manga is getting serialized the issue before yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You are high schoolers, I hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.13,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Its nice to be fresh-faced.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I was just thinking of taking them around to meet everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's tough for newcomers.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oishi, can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga should be interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,61!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 61!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have Bingo?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.15,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,It's number 61!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.15,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first winner, Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Which prize would you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... the TV.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The special prize right off the bat!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect, since the TV in our workplace is still analog.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.09,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a mangaka really is about\N hard work, self-confidence, and luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,More like hard work, conceit, and luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe we've used up our luck with this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you won't give the \Ngo ahead for an anime yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuujirou said that an anime will catch up to the manga soon, so I shouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unexpectedly cautious.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, will you give me your autograph?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my relatives is a fan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Who should I make it out to?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.19,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji looks like he's having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he delaying an anime adaptation?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already become a real, serious mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.99,0:20:26.20,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Niizuma! Talk to me more! Reassure me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we be like that too?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.53,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to come here every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll definitely come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.54,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, you need to work \Nhard on your serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Have you gotten\N a bit more settled?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The people here are really charismatic, and we got a bit overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a great opportunity. Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, there's an after party, and an after-after party!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only one high schoolers should attend.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give them undue temptations.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Editor-in-Chief!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, that was...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Mashirito!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mashiro and Takagi. Their serialization begins this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi Tarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him was a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As someone who worked with him, I can only feel regret.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man with guts.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that backfired on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.01,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to have the opportunity to serialize people like you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.89,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do what \Nmy uncle couldn't do,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.78,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the things he left undone.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What he couldn't do?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What he left undone?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What he couldn't do
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was make a living \Noff of manga alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What he left undone
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.30,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,was getting first\N place in the survey!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How promising.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The best chance of getting first place in the survey is in the first year of serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.94,0:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Popular mangakas want to get the top spot {\i1}and{\i0} have a long-running series.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibility isn't zero.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.59,0:22:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than thinking that, you think the possibilities are infinite.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of thinking \N"I'd like to make that a reality",
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.59,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you think "By my actions, I'll make it a reality."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that from some movie.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.27,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the party is in full swing,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.73,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.07,0:22:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.73,0:22:23.78,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,unfortunately it's about time to wrap things up.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.94,0:22:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.78,0:22:27.15,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,We reserved the hall for a short time...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.57,0:22:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Number one on the survey?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending a text to Azuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.12,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't forget the determination I had today!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.37,0:22:39.71,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Our serialization is about to start, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.14,0:24:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...our supervisor got changed, and then...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.77,0:24:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something else?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.68,0:24:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki, why did you send that text?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.77,0:24:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What text?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.02,0:24:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Anthologies and Photo Albums"
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.02,0:24:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is more important, dreams or reality?
